01:01:08,916 --> 01:01:11,919
that would help swing
the election against Lincoln.

1104
01:01:15,547 --> 01:01:19,426
But sherman's advance
was a masterpiece of planning.

1105
01:01:19,593 --> 01:01:21,261
In a matter of hours,

