01:01:31,897 --> 01:01:34,692
When Nathan bedford forrest's
raiders collapsed a tunnel

1109
01:01:34,858 --> 01:01:36,151
in sherman's rear,

1110
01:01:36,318 --> 01:01:38,654
one weary Southern private
was not impressed.

1111
01:01:38,821 --> 01:01:40,072
"Sherman," he said,

1112
01:01:40,239 --> 01:01:42,449
"probably carried
a spare tunnel with him."

