01:02:20,779 --> 01:02:23,657
and made good
progress today."

1125
01:02:23,824 --> 01:02:28,078
William tecumseh sherman.

1126
01:02:28,245 --> 01:02:30,330
At kennesaw mountain,
north of Atlanta,

1127
01:02:30,497 --> 01:02:32,374
the confederates dug in.

1128
01:02:32,541 --> 01:02:34,001
ON June 27th,

1129
01:02:34,168 --> 01:02:37,087
13,000 union men
stormed up the mountain

1130
01:02:37,254 --> 01:02:39,256
