repeated it either.

1146
01:03:22,132 --> 01:03:26,094
Reluctantly, he returned
to his slow flanking maneuvers,

1147
01:03:26,261 --> 01:03:28,180
forcing johnston
back to within sight

1148
01:03:28,347 --> 01:03:30,224
